class.name: gd_Graphic3d_NameOfTexturePlane
class.brief_description: Wrapper for the OpenCASCADE Graphic3d_NameOfTexturePlane enum.
class.description:
This class exposes the Graphic3d_NameOfTexturePlane enum to Godot. Represents the type of the texture projection plane for both S and T texture coordinates.
Note: This is an enum wrapper only; no instance methods are provided.
